Package Ex1

Class ComplexFunction

java.lang.Object
Ex1.ComplexFunction
All Implemented Interfaces:
Ex1.complex_function, Ex1.function, java.io.Serializable
public class ComplexFunction
extends java.lang.Object
implements Ex1.complex_function
This interface represents a complex function of type y=g(f1(x), f2(x)), where both f1, f2 are functions (or complex functions), y and x are real numbers and g is an operation: plus, mul, div, max, min, comp (f1(f2(x))).
